cosc345.app.model

Class FFT

  • java.lang.Object
    • cosc345.app.model.FFT
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable

    public class FFT
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Runnable
    A class that takes mic input from an Android device and uses a variation of the Fast Fourier Transformation to convert that input into a frequency.

    Code adapted from https://github.com/eresid/android-guitar-tuner
